Putri Ambika Singhania.

00:09:22.088 --> 00:09:23.111
Dia benar.

00:09:24.089 --> 00:09:25.205
Dia bukan istriku.

00:09:25.230 --> 00:09:28.207
Maafkan aku, aku
pikir kamu mungkin...

00:09:28.503 --> 00:09:30.652
